<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<!--
    Block the Biotech "Old Mechanitor Compound" quest.

    That is the Biotech OpportunitySite_AncientComplex_Mechanitor QuestScriptDef (rootSelectionWeight 0
    + isRootSpecial, so never from the random roll; its name rules turn "complex" into "compound", so it
    renders in-game as "Old mechanitor compound"). It is fired by a
    StorytellerCompProperties_MechanitorComplexQuest comp on the shared abstract BaseStoryteller
    (incident GiveQuest_AncientComplex_Mechanitor, mtbDays 60). Removing that comp (patches run before
    def inheritance, so it propagates to every storyteller, The Antagonist included) suppresses it. The
    MechanitorShip quest that comp merely lists as a blocker is not fired here and is left intact.

    Global by nature (inherited base comp, not scoped to one storyteller); any already-queued compound
    quest in a save finishes on its own.
-->
<Patch>
    <Operation Class="PatchOperationRemove">
        <xpath>Defs/StorytellerDef[@Name="BaseStoryteller"]/comps/li[incident="GiveQuest_AncientComplex_Mechanitor"]</xpath>
    </Operation>
</Patch>
